{"tid":1325113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌你老母 唔撚該你地幫幫手","createTime":"2019-07-16T18:38:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T10:18:21.000Z","uid":238697,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b2706cffc55b6e747333fb1363c733b030cd3e6c","tid":1325113,"uid":238697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:38:00.000Z","msg":"揾機會幫自己屋企啲廢老del撚咗個email同fb <br />\n唔撚好再幫佢地開喇 見撚到幫死廢老講嘅野就炆<br />\n我真係好撚想佢地死 我地年青人用條命同前途嚟搏<br />\n想救返個香港 你班死廢老就係撚咁屌<br />\n日又屌 夜又屌 好似我地乜撚都錯咁<br />\n屌你老母 香港個未來我地架<br />\n班死廢老冇將來架喇 唔該你地做做野<br />\n直系親屬可能唔忍心割席 但係個啲姨媽姑姐就冇撚要啦<br />\n最撚憎啲八婆懶係有學識 扮撚哂有批判性思考咁<br />\n咪又係聽啲八婆鳩up<br />\n各位巴絲唔該幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36beebd695a8365ecf44ac8d54dd9c368f6c3262","tid":1325113,"uid":208931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:38:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\">唔理衝唔衝，七二一去金鐘</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">頭盔頭盔頭盔<br />\n<br />\n眼罩（泳鏡最撚掂） <br />\n<br />\n豬咀豬咀豬咀<br />\n<br />\n長遮長遮長遮<br />\n<br />\n 索帶索帶索帶<br />\n<br />\n長褲 <br />\n<br />\n鉸剪<br />\n<br />\n毛巾<br />\n<br />\n保鮮紙<br />\n<br />\n士巴拿 </span><br />\n<br />\n應承樓豬 會幫！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e80983d84563f948f0ce7f698e9d8bf34e0ead6","tid":1325113,"uid":238697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:42:22.000Z","msg":"推please"},{"pid":"46d4141714241cb30f20e6cdfbcfc613edb2096f","tid":1325113,"uid":31205,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:42:43.000Z","msg":"呢刻既我覺得 藍絲都算 起碼你有立場<br />\n經過呢個月 我最撚憎既係到呢一刻都淨係識飲飲食食post ig 打卡去玩果班仆街港豬<br />\n到呢刻都話自己政治冷感呀唔識政治果班死仆街"},{"pid":"3cab3b041b37dd8206097432a12001f26b80ec9f","tid":1325113,"uid":170872,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:55:26.000Z","msg":"呢個真，扮理性分析既藍絲，問多兩句連成因同問題重心係邊都唔知，再問就老羞成怒，&quot;總之出黎既就係搞事同暴力&quot;<br />\n我冇野講"},{"pid":"93de355792d4356e46b311e2e0117b3b38a46bdb","tid":1325113,"uid":136730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:59:34.000Z","msg":"早就同左老母講<br />\n我同啲姨媽姑姐唔熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以後飲茶食飯唔好再叫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過新年有利是就幫我拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n始終人地一番心意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5280a5ab0c18fe99f8a1a06f1bf9f54164c1c7","tid":1325113,"uid":238697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:01:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"518854a2f7289a9127428b3eebd7ea20700587c2","tid":1325113,"uid":238697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993ac65da70c9a62d7b02d6639bd9b810bcf5147","tid":1325113,"uid":260262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:18:17.000Z","msg":"岩呀屌 我老豆日屌夜屌 見我買把遮都話我去暴動 成撚日嘈嘈嘈"},{"pid":"41d2e0cf860a00f23ee0ce23e5cf358d18e3d89e","tid":1325113,"uid":238697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:22:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17526378f2e2e1baf9e91db035fbacc08ee036a7","tid":1325113,"uid":238697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:23:42.000Z","msg":"班廢老都唔睇email架啦<br />\nFb del撚咗佢 揾方法block埋個app佢<br />\n唔好俾佢地再毒害人喇"},{"pid":"e6e431d9e6edff3d8555c6805897df10a339b95b","tid":1325113,"uid":238697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:04:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66415f5c6d51f81efb0c0eec9fb514f4cfd20958","tid":1325113,"uid":238697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r